         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><head>Translation</head><p>To Lucius Volusius Bassus Carealis ,splendid man  <note>of senatorial status</note>, legate, a man of complete innocence and equity and equally of moderation; the people of Lepcis Magna, in accordance with a decree of the  council of the municipality, <supplied reason="subaudible">set this up</supplied> and to <supplied reason="subaudible">their</supplied> permanent patron .</p></div>
